title: The Deep End Part 6: Crashing In To You
description: The Sixth installment in the erotic romance series The Deep End; 'Crashing In To You' is a pre-qual of sorts and tells the story of Dave and Shelly Troy. Find out how they met and what brought them together. Learn more about the traumatic past of the Troy brothers, and meet them all... Pre-Nicole. If you are squeamish about controversial subject matter and graphic depictions of great sex, you may wan't to remain in shallower waters... But if you love a good sexy love story filled with controversy, hot alpha males, and the women who appreciate them just the way they are... come on... jump into The Deep End...
author: Lourie Nolan
